      <title>印度最有价值的抵押贷款机构面临竞争​​减弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/india-s-most-valuable-mortgage-lender-sees-competition-ebbing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴贾杰住房金融有限公司 (Bajaj Housing Finance Ltd.) 是印度市值最高的抵押贷款机构，周一首次公开交易后表现抢眼。随着大型银行退出零售领域，将重点转向需求正在回暖的企业信贷，该公司认为房地产市场的竞争正在缓和。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/india-s-most-valuable-mortgage-lender-sees-competition-ebbing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 06:56:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
